item.title: Steering Committee Meeting
item.description: Minutes from our last meeting on January 6, 2022, are now available at this link . The original committees from Tama and Toledo, and others who wish to join the effort, are invited to meet and discuss organization, priorities, and next steps. Agenda specifics: Discussion with Jon Werger from Wellmark Healthy Hometown.
